nnoremap <C-o>            gt
nnoremap <M-o>            gt
nnoremap <C-w><C-o>       :tabmove +1<CR>
nnoremap <C-b>            :nohl<CR><C-l>
nnoremap <C-n>            :set relativenumber!<CR>
nnoremap <leader><leader> :w<CR>
nnoremap <leader>a        :Ack!<space>
